This paper is about reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of neural networks (cs.LG) and programming languages (cs.PL) in representing policies. Additionally, the paper touches on the topic of verification (cs.SE) and transfer learning (cs.SY). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.AI and cs.LG, followed by cs.SE, cs.SY, and cs.PL.
